data.rationale:
This module implements the freenet client protocol
    (http://freenet.sourceforge.net/index.php?page=fcp).

    There is so far no freenet client protocoll implementation
    available in perl, and this module tries to set a base standard in
    the asynchroneous events etc. are handled in a manner compatible
    with existing Event mechanisms.
